Package: portmond-src
Version: 1.0
Architecture: armhf
Maintainer: P Bennett <bencomltd16@gmail.com>
Depends: pigpio
Installed-Size: 10 
Homepage: http://zlham.blogspot.com
Description: Portmond monitors Raspberry Pi GPIO for changes.
 Portmond sends a GET request to the web server named in /etc/portmond/portmon.conf. Use sudo systemctl enable portmond to enable. sudo kill -sSIGUSR1 $pid checks state of all ports.
